{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"removeAnnotation:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotation:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1820"},"role":"symbol"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation object to remove. This object must conform","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing an annotation object dissociates it from the map view entirely,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preventing it from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method only when you want to hide or delete a given annotation.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibr